description: The singer and guitarist was part of sibling quintet that took over the pop world in 1969 — it released four consecutive No. 1 hits — and launched a family entertainment dynasty that lasted decades.
title: Tito Jackson, member of the Jackson 5, dies at 70

description: A new film follows Trey Parker and Matt Stone as they renovate a dilapidated, inauthentic, 1970s Mexican restaurant. The labor of love becomes a money-pit as they chase the landmark's former glory.
title: 'South Park' creators renovate a beloved restaurant, and find nostalgia is pricey

description: The Bear, Shogun and Baby Reindeer split most of the major categories, while Eugene and Dan Levy did their best to move things along. There weren't many surprises and ... wait, didn't we just do this?
title: 5 takeaways from the 2024 Emmy awards
